"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?33/2/33829/abstract/13\">",
"      Schreiber S, Lawrance IC, Thomsen O&Oslash;, et al. Randomised clinical trial: certolizumab pegol for fistulas in Crohn's disease - subgroup results from a placebo-controlled study. Aliment Pharmacol Ther 2011; 33:185.",
"     </a>",
