"      Hanauer SB, Panes J, Colombel JF, et al. Clinical trial: impact of prior infliximab therapy on the clinical response to certolizumab pegol maintenance therapy for Crohn's disease. Aliment Pharmacol Ther 2010; 32:384.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
