"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?33/2/33829/abstract/16\">",
"      Allez M, Vermeire S, Mozziconacci N, et al. The efficacy and safety of a third anti-TNF monoclonal antibody in Crohn's disease after failure of two other anti-TNF antibodies. Aliment Pharmacol Ther 2010; 31:92.",
